name: Xenomaterial II - Consumption
description:
Alien Ecology Series

An alien material created using living organisms. It can be molded into any desired shape, and goes through the following steps: birth, consumption, decay, rebirth. It therefore needs to be replaced frequently, but can be grown and recycled at will.

Created by Fivos Doganis (@fdoganis) as a part of the Alien Ecology Series, a reflection on technology and life.
